{"tid":2100812,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有外國護照有閪屌","createTime":"2020-07-09T10:13:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-09T12:03:04.000Z","uid":297430,"like":8,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"c7dc373ce1598522148a4164c1f7ed9dcaee56f3","tid":2100812,"uid":297430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T10:13:30.000Z","msg":"【網民熱話】女友嫌棄冇能力移民 提分手結束7年感情<br />\n<br />\n最近香港湧現移民潮，有網民在討論區大吐苦水，指沒有能力移民，令女友大感不滿，最後提出分手，結束7年感情。一眾網民留言，發表對此事不同看法。有網民指英國現時推出5+1政策，移民其實不需要太多資本。<br />\n<br />\n另外有網民認為女方不應單依靠男方移民，應該自食其力，一起計劃移民，更認為事主應該與女友分手，因為擁有這樣的價值觀，關係維持下去也不會長久。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2688892/【網民熱話】女友嫌棄冇能力移民%20%20提分手結束7年感情\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2688892%2F%E3%80%90%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E7%86%B1%E8%A9%B1%E3%80%91%E5%A5%B3%E5%8F%8B%E5%AB%8C%E6%A3%84%E5%86%87%E8%83%BD%E5%8A%9B%E7%A7%BB%E6%B0%91%2520%2520%E6%8F%90%E5%88%86%E6%89%8B%E7%B5%90%E6%9D%9F7%E5%B9%B4%E6%84%9F%E6%83%85&d=LWtkxptWC%2F4RDCuqQUibmq7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=006e8548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2688892/【網民熱話】女友嫌棄冇能力移民%20%20提分手結束7年感情</a><br />\n<br />\n有護照有高潮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"555a8ef377d3e8e577f63d44159a5a7051a5f5db","tid":2100812,"uid":84102,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T10:35:49.000Z","msg":"呢啲閪女人 一齊咗七年先知對方無能力咩 嫌三嫌四就滾啦咁 你咁有本事識返個移到民既男人啦"},{"pid":"2a8eb464c85592f17878b4c9a731c014610bc029","tid":2100812,"uid":127425,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T10:39:54.000Z","msg":"有外國護照<br />\n有冇絲打想要<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\